name: @ionic-native/file-transfer
readme: Improve this doc # File Transfer ``` $ ionic cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-file-transfer $ npm install --save @ionic-native/file-transfer ``` ## [Usage Documentation](https://ionicframework.com/docs/native/file-transfer/) Plugin Repo: [https://github.com/apache/cordova-plugin-file-transfer](https://github.com/apache/cordova-plugin-file-transfer) This plugin allows you to upload and download files. ## Supported platforms - Amazon Fire OS - Android - Browser - iOS - Ubuntu - Windows - Windows Phone
